alse, "is_admin": false, "score": 85, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8708904, "raw_content": "", "author": "PatriotSam", "created": 1782940729118, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "MarshallB", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBhLJpv2.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/Elqmem5g0dzu.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/gqcbp6qgEFl9boMB.jpeg", "width": 768, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 714}], "blurhash": "U2Amb#-o00~CFrXnD%R*00?H~D9t^n-4-=-q", "full_resolution": [1004, 1080]}, "title": "Trump: On July 4th it's going to be 107\u00b0 out, and I'm going to make a long speech just to show I can do anything.", "last_comment_created": 1782941132132, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 1, "score_up": 85, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBhMR8NM", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8709520, "raw_content": "Recall that the only issue that mattered when selecting Amy Coney Barrett was ROE V WADE.\r\n\r\nIt is the only thing any pundit, scholar, or politician talked about. WE MUST SAVE DA BABIES!!!\r\n\r\nThe issue of birthright citizenship was not even mentioned once. In fact, it never became a point of debate at all until Trump boldly tried to overturn it with an executive order.\r\n\r\nWhen he did that, everyone laughed at him saying it would be a 9-0 decision against him. Turns out we were just one vote away and it was of course MRS ROE V WADE who screwed us.\r\n\r\nNow we have DeSantis faggots and other old blood conservatives trying to dunk on Trump for picking Barrett when it was literally all their idea to pick a justice who was 100% against Roe. They cared about NOTHING else. If it were entirely up to Trump he would have picked a radical anti immigration judge! He\u2019s not even very pro abortion. He was pressured into being anti-abortion at all costs by Republican retards.\r\n\r\nRetards like DeSantis were campaigning on a 5 week federal abortion ban \u2014 basically forfeiting the election and handing over the country to communists all so they could virtue signal. Now they want to blame Trump for birthright citizenship? **YOU ABORTION-OBSESSED RETARDS ARE LITERALLY WHY WE HAVE BIRTHRIGHT CITIZENSHIP**. Lmao. \r\n\r\nI personally think abortion is evil and if I were king I\u2019d ban it entirely. However, it is not the most important issue and it\u2019s an huge losing issue for Republicans that isn\u2019t worth the cost. Immigration is the most important issue (BY FAR). We have to fix that before anything else. Abortion-obsessed retards are why we\u2019re going to get 10 million new third world \u201ccitizens.\u201d \r\n\r\nFrankly, democrats killing their own kids (future libtards) is not the worst thing in the world. It\u2019s demonic to kill a baby but sadly that\u2019s where we are at right now. If abortion was totally banned democrats would have already taken over the country. The silver lining of this demonic evil is LESS DEMOCRATS. Now we have the worst of both worlds: unlimited third world citizenship + high birth rate for democrats.", "author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "created": 1782972062425, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "HBPAT4547", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Abortion puritans gave us birthright citizenship.", "last_comment_created": 1782976181433, "content": "<p>Recall that the only issue that mattered when selecting Amy Coney Barrett was ROE V WADE.</p>\n<p>It is the only thing any pundit, scholar, or politician talked about. WE MUST SAVE DA BABIES!!!</p>\n<p>The issue of birthright citizenship was not even mentioned once. In fact, it never became a point of debate at all until Trump boldly tried to overturn it with an executive order.</p>\n<p>When he did that, everyone laughed at him saying it would be a 9-0 decision against him. Turns out we were just one vote away and it was of course MRS ROE V WADE who screwed us.</p>\n<p>Now we have DeSantis faggots and other old blood conservatives trying to dunk on Trump for picking Barrett when it was literally all their idea to pick a justice who was 100% against Roe. They cared about NOTHING else. If it were entirely up to Trump he would have picked a radical anti immigration judge! He\u2019s not even very pro abortion. He was pressured into being anti-abortion at all costs by Republican retards.</p>\n<p>Retards like DeSantis were campaigning on a 5 week federal abortion ban \u2014 basically forfeiting the election and handing over the country to communists all so they could virtue signal. Now they want to blame Trump for birthright citizenship? <strong>YOU ABORTION-OBSESSED RETARDS ARE LITERALLY WHY WE HAVE BIRTHRIGHT CITIZENSHIP</strong>. Lmao.</p>\n<p>I personally think abortion is evil and if I were king I\u2019d ban it entirely. However, it is not the most important issue and it\u2019s an huge losing issue for Republicans that isn\u2019t worth the cost. Immigration is the most important issue (BY FAR). We have to fix that before anything else. Abortion-obsessed retards are why we\u2019re going to get 10 million new third world \u201ccitizens.\u201d</p>\n<p>Frankly, democrats killing their own kids (future libtards) is not the worst thing in the world. It\u2019s demonic to kill a baby but sadly that\u2019s where we are at right now. If abortion was totally banned democrats would have already taken over the country. The silver lining of this demonic evil is LESS DEMOCRATS. Now we have the worst of both worlds: unlimited third world citizenship + high birth rate for democrats.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 18, "score_up": 17, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2072011300125778387", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBhMQ2Nj", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 50, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "treason", "id": 8709157, "raw_content": "", "author": "CleanUpPhillyTrump24", "created": 1782950957169, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Zennblack", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBhMQ2Nj.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/JacSarobahs/status/2072011300125778387", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "This is not domestic politics. It's a foreign operation to undermine the US on July 4th: sophisticated algae grow labs and paint devouring peptides in ultrasonic hydroponics rigs found in storage units are tied to Antifa, says FBI. Cartels already have this expertise so that's my guess.", "last_comment_created": 1782951821400, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text"